<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>구매한 아이템 목록 - 몽글몽글</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=SUIT:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'SUIT', sans-serif;
            background-color: #fef6f0;
            margin: 0;
        }
        header {
            background: #fff;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 0.4rem 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
        header .logo img {
            height: 80px;
            margin-right: 0.75rem;
        }
        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            flex: 1;
        }
        nav a {
            margin-left: 1rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #555;
            font-weight: 500;
            padding: 0.3rem 0.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(transparent 60%, #fff3b0 60%);
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            color: #ff8243;
        }
        main {
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 2rem auto;
            padding: 2rem;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        h2 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #444;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .item-box {
            background-color: #fff6ea;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
        .item-name {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #444;
        }
        .item-detail {
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 0.3rem;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }
        .empty {
            text-align: center;
            color: #999;
        }
        .user-info {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.6rem;
}

.nickname {
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #555;
  white-space: nowrap;
}

.logout-btn {
  background-color: #ffc1a1;
  color: white;
  font-weight: 600;
  padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 20px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background-color 0.3s;
}

.logout-btn:hover {
  background-color: #ffa577;
}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
    <div class="logo">
        <img src="/images/image.png" alt="몽글몽글">
    </div>
    <nav>
        <a href="/write">일기 작성</a>
        <a href="/diarylist">일기 목록</a>
        <a href="/store">스토어</a>
        <a href="/mypayments">구매 목록</a>
        <a href="/emotion/report">감정 리포트</a>
        <a href="/api/user/me">마이페이지</a>
    </nav>
    <div class="user-info">
        <span class="nickname">{{nickname}} 님</span>
        <form action="/logout" method="post">
            <button class="logout-btn" type="submit">로그아웃</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</header>

<main>
    <h2>구매한 아이템 목록 🛒</h2>

    {{^payments}}
        <div class="empty">구매한 아이템이 아직 없어요 ☁️</div>
    {{/payments}}

    {{#payments}}
        <div class="item-box">
            <div class="item-name">{{item.itemName}}</div>
            <div class="item-detail">
                가격: ₩ {{amount}} · 결제일: {{paidAt}}
            </div>
        </div>
    {{/payments}}
</main>
</body>
</html>
